msgstr "当前查询"

msgid ""
"Note that only candidates which you have permission to access in LORIS are "
"included in results. Number of results may vary from other users running the"
" same query."
msgstr "请注意，结果中仅包含您有权在 LORIS 中访问的候选人。结果数量可能与运行相同查询的其他用户不同。"

