msgstr "至少进行一次以下访问"

msgid ""
"This field may exist multiple times for a single {{scope}}. Adding a "
"criteria based on it means that it must match for <italic>at least "
"one</italic> of the data points."
msgstr "对于单个 {{scope}} ，该字段可能存在多次。基于它添加一个条件意味着它必须匹配<斜体>至少一个</斜体>数据点。"

msgid ""
"This field may exist multiple times for a single {{scope}} and must match "
"for *any* of the data points"
msgstr "对于单个 {{scope}}，此字段可能存在多次，并且必须与*任何*数据点匹配"

