msgid ""
"Above, there is also a Study Queries panel. This are a special type of "
"shared queries that have been pinned by a study administer to always display"
" at the top of this page."
msgstr "上面还有一个研究查询面板。这是一种特殊类型的共享查询，研究管理员已将其固定为始终显示在此页面的顶部。"

msgid ""
"The data query tool allows you to query data within LORIS. There are three "
"steps to defining a query:"
msgstr "数据查询工具允许您查询LORIS内的数据。定义查询分为三个步骤："

msgid ""
"First, you must select the fields that you're interested in on the Define "
"Fields page."
msgstr "首先，您必须在“定义字段”页面上选择您感兴趣的字段。"

msgid ""
"Next, you can optionally define filters on the Define Filters page to "
"restrict the population that is returned."
msgstr "接下来，您可以选择在“定义过滤器”页面上定义过滤器，以限制返回的总体。"

msgid ""
"The Next Steps on the bottom right of your screen always the context-"
"sensitive next steps that you can do to build your query."
msgstr "屏幕右下角的后续步骤始终是您可以用来构建查询的上下文相关的后续步骤。"

msgid "Finally, you view your query results on the View Data page"
msgstr "最后在查看数据页面查看查询结果"

msgid ""
"Your recently run queries will be displayed in the Recent Queries panel "
"below. Instead of building a new query, you can reload a query that you've "
"recently run by clicking on the icon next to the query."
msgstr "您最近运行的查询将显示在下面的“最近查询”面板中。您可以通过单击查询旁边的图标来重新加载最近运行的查询，而不是构建新查询。"

msgid ""
"Queries can be shared with others by clicking the icon. This will cause the "
"query to be shared with all users who have access to the fields used by the "
"query. It will display in a Shared Queries panel below the Recent Queries."
msgstr "通过单击图标可以与其他人共享查询。这将导致查询与有权访问该查询所使用的字段的所有用户共享。它将显示在“最近查询”下方的“共享查询”面板中。"

msgid ""
"You may also give a query a name at any time by clicking the icon. This "
"makes it easier to find queries you care about by giving them an easier to "
"remember name that can be used for filtering. When you share a query, the "
"name will be shared along with it."
msgstr ""
"您还可以随时通过单击图标为查询指定名称。通过为查询提供一个更容易记住、可用于过滤的名称，可以更轻松地找到您关心的查询。当您共享查询时，名称将随之共享。"

